<h2>How to Build Your Email List</h2>
<p>Most agents start with the wrong list. They buy a database of 10,000 contacts, blast a generic email, and get flagged as spam. A list of 500 people who actually want to hear from you will outperform a purchased list of 50,000 every time.</p>
<h3>Lead Magnets That Work for Real Estate</h3>
<p>Offer something valuable in exchange for an email address. The best lead magnets solve a specific problem for a specific audience.</p>
<p><strong>For buyers:</strong>
- First-time homebuyer checklist (PDF download)
- "5 Neighborhoods Under $400K in [City]" guide
- Mortgage pre-approval calculator
- Weekly new listing alerts for specific zip codes</p>
<p><strong>For sellers:</strong>
- Free home valuation tool
- "10 Renovations That Add the Most Value" guide
- Neighborhood market report (monthly)
- "How to Stage Your Home in a Weekend" checklist</p>
<p><strong>For investors:</strong>
- Rental yield calculator for [City]
- Monthly cap rate report by neighborhood
- "Due Diligence Checklist for Investment Properties" PDF</p>
