<h3>List Hygiene Rules</h3>
<p>A dirty list kills deliverability. Clean your list every 90 days:</p>
<ul>
<li>Remove hard bounces immediately</li>
<li>Remove contacts who have not opened in 6+ months (or send a re-engagement campaign first)</li>
<li>Verify new email addresses with a double opt-in</li>
<li>Never buy email lists. Ever. The contacts did not consent, and major email providers will penalize your sender reputation.</li>
</ul>
